'''Vincha''' was a [[Plant/Legends|plant]] with tubercles, which had incredible anesthetic proprieties. Vincha tubercles were [[Color/Legends|white]], not bigger than one's [[Limb/Legends|thumb]], and highly esteemed by [[Dantari]] people.

